#. Tag: title
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Opties"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following options apply to all &Qt; applications:"
msgstr "De volgende opties zijn van toepassing op alle &Qt;-applicaties:"

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-style=</option> <replaceable>style</replaceable> / <option>-style</"
"option> <replaceable>style</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-style=</option> <replaceable>stijl</replaceable> / <option>-style</"
"option> <replaceable>stijl</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the application &GUI; style. Possible values depend on the system "
"configuration. If &Qt; is compiled with additional styles or has additional "
"styles as plugins these will be available to the <option>-style</option> "
"command line option."
msgstr ""
"Stelt de stijl van de &GUI; van de toepassing in. Mogelijke waarden hangen "
"af van de systeemconfiguratie. Als &Qt; gecompileerd is met extra stijlen of "
"extra stijlen heeft als plug-ins dan zullen deze beschikbaar zijn in de "
"optie <option>-style</option> van de commandoregel."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-stylesheet=</option> <replaceable>stylesheet</replaceable> / "
"<option>-stylesheet</option> <replaceable>stylesheet</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-stylesheet=</option> <replaceable>stijlsheet</replaceable> / "
"<option>-stylesheet</option> <replaceable>stijlsheet</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the application styleSheet. The value must be a path to a file that "
"contains the Style Sheet."
msgstr ""
"Stel styleSheet van de toepassing in. De waarde moet een pad zijn naar een "
"bestand dat de Style Sheet bevat."

#. Tag: option
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "-widgetcount"
msgstr "-widgetcount"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Print debug message at the end about number of widgets left undestroyed and "
"maximum number of widgets existed at the same time."
msgstr ""
"Toont aan het eind een debugbericht over het aantal widgets dat niet "
"vernietigd is achtergelaten en het maximum aantal widgets dat tegelijk "
"bestond."

#. Tag: option
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "-reverse"
msgstr "-reverse"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the application's layout direction to <methodname>Qt::RightToLeft</"
"methodname>. This option is intended to aid debugging and should not be used "
"in production. The default value is automatically detected from the user's "
"locale (see also <methodname>QLocale::textDirection()</methodname>)."
msgstr ""
"Stelt de richting in van de indeling van de toepassing naar <methodname>Qt::"
"RightToLeft</methodname>. Deze optie is bedoeld om te helpen bij het "
"debuggen en zou in productie niet gebruikt moeten worden. De standaard "
"waarde wordt automatisch gedetecteerd uit de instelling van de taalregio van "
"de gebruiker (zie ook <methodname>QLocale::textDirection()</methodname>)."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-qmljsdebugger=</option> <replaceable>port</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-qmljsdebugger=</option> <replaceable>poort</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Activate the QML/JS debugger with a specified port. The value must be of "
"format port:1234[,block], where block is optional and will make the "
"application wait until a debugger connects to it."
msgstr ""
"Activeer de QML/JS debugger met een gespecificeerde poort. De waarde moet "
"het format port:1234[,block] hebben, waar block optioneel is en maakt dat de "
"toepassing zal wachten totdat een debugger er een verbinding naar maakt."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-platform</option> <replaceable>platformName[:options]</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-platform</option> <replaceable>platformNaam[:opties]</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify the &Qt; Platform Abstraction (QPA) plugin."
msgstr "Specificeer de plug-in &Qt; Platform Abstraction (QPA)."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-platformpluginpath</option> <replaceable>path</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-platformpluginpath</option> <replaceable>pad</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify the path to platform plugins."
msgstr "Het pad naar de platform-plug-ins instellen"

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-platformtheme</option> <replaceable>platformTheme</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-platformtheme</option> <replaceable>platformThema</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify the platform theme."
msgstr "Het platformthema instellen."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-plugin</option> <replaceable>plugin</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-plugin</option> <replaceable>plug-in</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify additional plugins to load. The argument may appear multiple times."
msgstr ""
"Stel extra te laden plug-ins in. Het argument mag meerdere keren verschijnen."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-qwindowgeometry</option> <replaceable>geometry</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-qwindowgeometry</option> <replaceable>geometrie</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify the window geometry for the main window using the &X11;-syntax. For "
"example: -qwindowgeometry 100x100+50+50"
msgstr ""
"Specificeer de geometrie van het venster voor het hoofdvenster met de &X11;-"
"syntaxis. Bijvoorbeeld: -qwindowgeometry 100x100+50+50"

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-qwindowicon</option> <replaceable>icon</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-qwindowicon</option> <replaceable>pictogram</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the default window icon."
msgstr "Het standaard vensterpictogram instellen."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-qwindowtitle</option> <replaceable>title</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-qwindowtitle</option> <replaceable>titel</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the title of the first window."
msgstr "Stel de titel in van het eerste venster."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-session</option> <replaceable>session</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-session</option> <replaceable>sessie</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restore the application from an earlier session."
msgstr "De toepassing herstellen uit een eerdere sessie."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-display</option> <replaceable>hostname:screen_number</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-display</option> <replaceable>hostnaam:schermnummer</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch displays on &X11;. Overrides the <envar>DISPLAY</envar> environment "
"variable."
msgstr ""
"Schakel schermen over op &X11;. Overschrijft de omgevingsvariabele "
"<envar>DISPLAY</envar>."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-geometry</option> <replaceable>geometry</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-geometry</option> <replaceable>geometie</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify the window geometry for the main window on &X11;. For example: -"
"geometry 100x100+50+50"
msgstr ""
"Specificeer de geometrie van het venster voor het hoofdvenster op &X11;. "
"Bijvoorbeeld: -qwindowgeometry 100x100+50+50"

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-dialogs=</option> <replaceable>[xp|none]</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-dialogs=</option> <replaceable>[xp|none]</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only available for the &Windows; platform. XP uses native style dialogs and "
"none disables them."
msgstr ""
"Alleen beschikbaar voor platform &Windows;. XP gebruikt eigen stijldialogen "
"en niets schakelt ze uit."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-fontengine=</option> <replaceable>freetype</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-fontengine=</option> <replaceable>freetype</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the FreeType font engine."
msgstr "Gebruik de lettertype-engine FreeType."

#. Tag: option
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "-h, --help and -? on &Windows;"
msgstr "-h, --help en -? on &Windows;"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print all options and the application description."
msgstr "Alle opties en de beschrijving van de toepassing tonen."

#. Tag: option
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v --version"
msgstr "-v --version"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the version string of the application."
msgstr "Toont tekenreeks met de versie-informatie van de toepassing."

#. Tag: title
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "See Also"
msgstr "Zie ook"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "<replaceable>kf6options</replaceable>(7)"
msgstr "<replaceable>kf6opties</replaceable>(7)"

#. Tag: title
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "Authors"
msgstr "Auteurs"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid "Man page originally written by &Lauri.Watts; &Lauri.Watts.mail;"
msgstr ""
"Manpagina oorspronkelijk geschreven door &Lauri.Watts; &Lauri.Watts.mail;"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Updated to &frameworks; 5 by &Burkhard.Lueck; &Burkhard.Lueck.mail;"
msgstr ""
"Bijgewerkt naar &frameworks; door &Burkhard.Lueck; &Burkhard.Lueck.mail;"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
